      "This example illustrates why importers who estimate landed cost as simply 'product cost + 20% duty' consistently underestimate their true costs. The actual landed cost increase of 36.2% over FOB value is nearly double the basic duty rate of 10%, once all freight, tax, and handling components are included.",
      "## How FTWZ Optimises Your Landed Cost",
